Fwd Gore I Am by Dr Suess okay really its by PhilForwarded by Eve PuckettCorpEnron on AM Angela CT AM To Judy CT Regina NRON Eve NRON Judy CT Mark D CT cc Subject Fwd Gore I Am by Dr Suess okay really its by Phil Forwarded by Angela BarnettHOUECT on AM on PM To cc Subject Fwd Gore I Am by Dr Suess okay really its by Phil just a little somethin a friend sent it was too cute to hold on to o ContentTransferEncoding bit Returnpath From Fullname HisevrNow MessageID Date Fri Nov EST Subject Gore I Am by Dr Suess okay really its by Phil To MIMEVersion ContentType textplain charsetUSASCII XMailer Windows AOL sub Its beginning to get embarrassing how many things are out there ridiculing this now everpresent election But way too many of them are too funny to keep to oneself by Phil Can we count them with our nose Can we count them with our toes Should we count them with a band Should we count them all by hand If I do not like the count I will simply throw them out I will not let this vote count stand I do not like them AL GORE I am Can we change these numbers here Can we change them calm my fears What do you mean Dubya has won This is not fair this is not fun Lets count them upside down this time Lets count until the state is mine I will not let this VOTE count stand I do not like it AL GORE I am Im really ticked Im in a snit You have not heard the last of it Ill count the ballots one by one And hold each one up to the sun Ill count recount and count some more Youll grow to hate this little chore But I will not cannot let this vote count stand I do not like it Al Gore I am I wont leave office Im stayin here Ive glued my desk chair to my rear Tipper Hillary and Bubba too all telling me that I should sue We find the Electoral College vile RECOUNT the votes until I smile We do not want this vote to stand We do not like it AL GORE I am How shall we count this ballot box Lets count it standing in our socks Shall we count this one in a tree And who shall count it you or me We cannot cannot count enough We must not stop we must be tough I do not want this vote to stand I do not like it AL GORE I am Ive counted till my fingers bleed And still cant fulfill my counting need Ill count the tiles on the floor Ill count and count and count some more And I will not say that I am done Until the counting says Ive won I will not let this vote count stand I do not like it AL GORE I am Whats that What What are you trying to say You think the current count should stay You do not like my counting scheme It makes you tense gives you bad dreams Foolish people youre wrong youll see Youre only care should be for me I WILL NOT LET THIS VOTE COUNT STAND I DO NOT LIKE IT AND AL GORE I AM

Work PerformanceForwarded by Eve PuckettCorpEnron on PM From Eve Puckett PM To Brenna NRON cc Leslie CT Regina NRON Diane nron Lois NRON Sharon NRON Angela CT Angela nron Subject Work Performance Brenna This probably isnt the best time to be mentioning this and I dont want you to think there is any motive behind it because reviews are currently in process but I wanted to briefly talk to you about Judy Hernandez I think she puts in a great work performance for many reasons She is ALWAYS willing to help out when someone is backed up on projects If you ask her to help you out with something its completed within the same day or early the next day She is NEVER in a bad mood and if she is she certainly doesnt let you know about it nor take out her frustrations on anyone She is very knowledgeable when it comes to questions about deals being acceptable or not If she cant answer your question she points you in the right direction for it to be answered I just wanted to let you know how much I appreciate working with her ThanksEve
